asset.author: Everlast
asset.hookText: Cara Castronuova, Season 11 Biggest Loser Trainer, is excited about partnering up with Everlast and the fight against breast cancer because she has a lot of survivors against breast cancer in her family. Everlast will donate part of the proceeds of sales from select products towards the Breast Cancer Research Foundation. To view the products click here: http://www.shopeverlast.com/women-support-breast-cancer-research.html
